From git@z Thu Jan  1 00:00:00 1970
Subject: [PATCH 3/21] drm/amd/display: Add required FRL registers for DCN31
From: Rodrigo Siqueira <Rodrigo.Siqueira@amd.com>
Date: Fri, 01 May 2026 10:04:19 -0400
Message-Id: <20260501140441.41068-4-harry.wentland@amd.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset="utf-8"
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit

This commit introduces multiple hardware registers necessary to enable
FRL on AMD devices.

Signed-off-by: Rodrigo Siqueira <Rodrigo.Siqueira@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Harry Wentland <harry.wentland@amd.com>
---
